  "title": "Despatch Rider",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Delivery of confidential documents</li><li>Collection of Information</li><li>Any other duties which may be assigned from time to time</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>1) Possess class 2A/2B driving license with own motor vehicle<br />2) Clean driving record<br />3) Able to converse and write in English<br />4) Familiar with Singapore roads</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Work Schedule:</strong></p><ul><li>11am to 8pm (Monday to Saturday)</li><li>2 weekdays off</li><li>Flexible timing</li><li>Own time own target</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p>1) Productivity incentives<br />2) Commission<br />3) Full CPF Contribution<br />4) Annual Leave/ Medical Leave/ Medical Claim/ Paternity Leave/ Maternity Leave/ Childcare Leave<br />5) Birthday Leave<br />6) Referral program</p>",
